                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-32-off155 t17880402-32-cd156"></join> last, one earthen-ware dish, value 6 d. and thirty-two pounds weight of salted butter, value 17 s. 4 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880402-32-victim359" type="victimName">
