                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>On the 14th of March, the prisoner came into the shop, about a quarter before nine in the morning, and took a dish of salt butter from off the counter, and ran off; I cried out, stop thief! he dropped the butter; I pursued him, and took him; he never was out of my sight; my wife picked up the butter.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178804020054"></xptr>
            
